==Pronunciation==
[[IPA]]: /ə'skep pɔd/

==[[Noun]]==
# Any small, secondary, emergency-use vehicle used to [[evacuate]] from the main vehicle during times of danger. Usually refers to a small pod-like [[capsule]] that fits a low number of people. Escape pods are common in science-fiction literature, and often are attached to [[spaceship]]s, although marine varieties have been spotted.